Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:17.69,Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Note: The Kan'ei Era was from 1624 to 1643.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even when the drought of the{\i}\N{\i1}Kan'ei Era came to pay us a visit,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}this well had remained unperturbed, but now...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, good sir from Aoi-ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Oshige, how do you fare?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The rainy season has yet to come,\Nbut the heat is fierce.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be dreadful if it fails to rain soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People are praying for rain...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What has happened to the Eastern rain?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Chief of Internal Affairs{\i}\N{\i1}was assassinated in Tokyo...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one who struck him down{\i}\N{\i1}was Soujiro Seta of the Shishio Faction.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What of Makoto Shishio?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.23,0:00:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sir, he and several subordinates{\i}\N{\i1}have come to Kyoto.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to trouble you with this upon\Nyour arrival in Kyoto, Officer Fujita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto Shishio. Born in Shingetsu Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(290,176)}DAILY KYOTO NEWSPAPER{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He was allied with the Choshu Faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This man inherited his predecessor's job\Nto slay men from the shadows."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought that he was killed\Nin the Boshin War.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto Shishio is a treacherous individual
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,whose lust for ambition and conquest\Nis beyond comprehension for normal men.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.93,0:01:30.75,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(508,222)}MAY 1878\NNO. 4\NREPORT ON MAKOTO SHISHIO\NKYOTO POLICE DEPARTMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.93,0:01:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,whose lust for ambition and conquest\Nis beyond comprehension for normal men.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of his assassinations were\Nof such great import
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that if brought to light, they could uproot\Nthe foundation of the Meiji government."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Had Shishio survived to greet the new era,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a possibility that he would\Ntake advantage of such weaknesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,allowing him to hold Japan\Nin the palm of his hand."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.95,0:01:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, the government took advantage of the\Nchaos in the Boshin War to dispose of him."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It claims that they doused his\Ncorpse in oil and set it aflame...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.06,0:02:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but he still managed to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He may indeed be... a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Absorbed in his hatred and\Ndesire for vengeance,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,he has forgotten that he is human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, HE will most likely be\Nthe key to defeating Shishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.97,0:02:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When he moves,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so moves the era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Aoshi has been missing since?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The person Aoshi encountered while in Tokyo...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That man is also making his way to Kyoto.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. He must be chasing after Shishio as well.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you know of him?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, his name is...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Misao! As a member of the\Nonmitsu group Oniwabanshu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,could you try to eavesdrop on a\Nconversation or two more eloquently?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me! Tell me about the guy\Nwho was with Master Aoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I find him, I'll find Master Aoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...Himura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kenshin...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let you handle subduing{\i}\N{\i1}Shishio all on your own!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:31.28,Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Note: Hitokiri - literally "Man cutter" or Manslayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hitokiri Battousai...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it is still in you to speak of restorations,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sing of this nation's future. I dare you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:46.90,Style 2,,0,0,60,,{\an8\i1\c&H1700E6&\3c&HFFFFFF&}RUROUNI KENSHIN\NNEW KYOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:50.83,Style 2,,0,0,60,,{\an8\i1}CAGE OF FLAMES
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Himura... Battousai!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm just fine, Lu No. 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I get that you're afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we're going up\Nagainst Himura Battousai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Formerly a revolutionary for the Choshu Faction,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,he was feared as the "Hitokiri Battousai"\Nduring the end of the Shogunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly the land of death\Nspreads to wherever he goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A cross-shaped scar?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's short and skinny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that wimpy-looking guy really Himura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! As a member of the Oniwabanshu,\NI must first confirm that he is the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Lu No. 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lu No. 1?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you are tickling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe Lu No. 1\Nwarmed up to him just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.97,0:05:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, what did you need with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura Battousai, spill it!\NWhere is Master Aoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He IS in the onmitsu Oniwabanshu\Nthat defended the lmperial Castle in Edo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How the heck... did you get across this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't let him go!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know what your relationship to Aoshi is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but down the path of pandemonium,\Ndanger is always by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you to tell me that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You should sever your feelings\Nfor the man and forget about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It is for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare give me that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I CAN'T forget him!\NThat's why I'm searching for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be crazy! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How the heck could forgetting about the person\NI care for the most make me happy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Until you tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't leave your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Straight ahead, there is a manor-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that where Master Aoshi is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto Shishio is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:08:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The man we sent on reconnaissance claims\Nto have seen Himura Battousai at Hakone Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, that is where he lost sight of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What became of that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wound up killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Seta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being most unseemly. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The hot springs located here in\NShingetsu Village soothes my burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It also tightens the ladies where it matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A-and where does it matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe this was the village of your birth,\Nwas it not, Makoto Shishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what I'd expect of my predecessor.\NYou know me well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shingetsu Village was exploited by the\Ngovernment, turning it into a ghost town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even this therapeutic hot springs resort
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,was an unfortunate legacy\Nthat financially destroyed the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This village reflects the true\Nshape of the Meiji government.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And my body reflects its true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,However, my motive is hardly\Nsomething as trivial as vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What I seek is power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to create a powerful country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Our current world is a façade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though the Shogunate was replaced by\Na bureaucracy, nothing has actually changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They use false pretenses of peace as bait,\Ngrow fat on their profits,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and secretly dispose of any\Nthey find to be a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,These are stopgap measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The government is rotten to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to create a new world that\Nis not a façade, strong power is-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You plan to destroy this country yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you may pluck the government\Nfrom its roots and plant a new seed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. This body has\Nmade me accept the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The ruling law of our world is that\N"the strong eat the flesh of the weak."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I shall use my power\Nto destroy all indolence...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...and burn away all falsehood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This false world may be the one to writhe in\Nagony as you engulf it in those flames,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but I cannot allow you to fill this era
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,with the screams of the innocent-\Nof those currently living in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sword... Didn't Shakku Arai\Nforge it in his final days?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The same is true of this one.\NIn other words, they are brother swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Shakku filled my sword with an\Ninfinitely pure bloodlust
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when he forged this blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In comparison, your sword that cannot kill\Nis no different than our current era.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It is merely a product of confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Our swords match their owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In which case, the relationship you and I share\Nis that of brothers who are complete opposites.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, play with him in my stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It is too soon for a\Nshowdown between "brothers."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I shall do as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Sou be all right on his own?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. His strength comes\Ndirectly from his lack of emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you can't read his mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pitted against Hiten Mitsurugi-ryuu,\Nhe could prove to be the ultimate foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Battou-jutsu, which would give him the lead,\Nmay prove effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But lacking the emotion "sadness,"\Nmurder does not trouble Soujiro's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How will the Battousai and his tepid resolve\Nto not kill fare against such a blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he is no longer the Battousai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It is clear how this battle will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory goes to me, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wow, this is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I care. This belongs to Shishio anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There were no winners or losers in this bout.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I must take my leave for today,\Nbut please fight me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to get another sword\Nbefore that time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that Shakku is still amongst the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not mind staying where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you didn't have the funds to cover two rooms,\Nwe didn't have to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In your search for me, you never\Nstopped running, not even to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your feet cannot take much more...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't patronize me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not patronizing you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are! If everything was right in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be a kunoichi,\Nworking by Master Aoshi's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I could tell going by your stances.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:13:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way you could possibly\Nlose to that Soujiro guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that you can't kill.\NAnd then there's that sakabatou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you seriously trying not to kill anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He called you his predecessor.\NWho is this Makoto Shishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because of me...\Nthat his fate was thrown askew.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If one darkness were to vanish,\Nthere would be need for a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I understood that, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The night birds... are hooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I... For some reason, I've been afraid\Nof the night ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I was with Master Aoshi,\NI could handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aoshi always goes on ahead,\Ntelling me what lies ahead in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I never told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Misao! I'm Misao Makimachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you continue to meddle\Nin my affairs, Miss Misao,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it will only feed the darkness\Nthat frightens you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's for Master Aoshi, I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm doing him any favors or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:33.24,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(652,392)}FOUND HIMURA BATTOUSAI.\NLOOK FOR A MASTER SWORDSMITH.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have to find out about\Nthis Shishio guy anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lu No. 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives?! Why isn't there a\Nsingle teahouse around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahiko, that sounds pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we got off at Owari Port!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You should find out what the destination\Nis when you pick out a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:14:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is part of our training.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As we are right now,\Nwouldn't we only get in Kenshin's way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe we shouldn't have\Ncome to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! C'mon! You look pathetic, Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your feet aren't moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, he's got a bunch of stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all pottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But, dang, this is covered in cracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,These suck. He stinks at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It broke, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I am sorry. We came inside\Nwithout your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:16:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The veins of pottery teach us\Nthe laws of the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw. I dropped it 'cause you startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But sorry about that-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall pay with your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So hot! You're burning me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay! I don't care if I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! I will force you to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This heat is the warmth of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall use it to burn away\Nthe rotten government!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,With the heat of life, I will bring Kyoto\Nand our lethargic era to a boil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To think you planned your strike\Nfor when I was enjoying myself, Usui.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly! My Mind's Eye cannot\Nperceive actions of this nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.02,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(586,182)}MIND'S EYE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It merely worked out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a job for you since you\Nhave interrupted our fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajime Saito, a former member of the\NShinsengumi, is sniffing around our trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And Himura Battousai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not interested in one soon to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That man still hopes to take\Nyour life, Master Shishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where those with power gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There are those who I have saved,\Nthose who serve me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,those who rely on me, those who use me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and those who are burning with the desire to\Nkill me after suffering defeat by my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But only true power, even if it be evil,\Ncould keep this group together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Shishio...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who are strong live,\Nand those who are weak die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, I simply need to be the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing may strike fear into the man who will\Nburn down the era with the flame called "power."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shakku's last sword, ya say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:18:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, although I am certain\Nhe will catch wind of it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What say you, Chou?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it stir your blood as a sword collector?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet, but there is no way Shishio's\Ngonna let me face Himura Battousai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Do as you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was not Himura's sakabatou that broke,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but his beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misao, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine! Just you leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lu No. 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Okina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shakku had a son with whom\Nhe entrusted all of his arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Seiku Arai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:52.20,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(1080,192)}SMITHY\NREPAIRS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry, but may I turn\Ndown that commission?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My father used to say, " I will create\Na new world with my swords."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But the swords my father created\Nunder that philosophy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,stole the lives of many who carried\Nthe weight of the new era.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it is the Meiji Era.\NThe age of peace has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Samurai have abandoned their swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, I wish to abandon\Nmy work as a swordsmith.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an age of peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you making?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it is a pellet drum for Iori, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I'm embarrassed\Nby how poorly it turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't seem to have a knack for it\Nlike I do forging blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a little bent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for having asked the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall take our leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but, hey! What are you going\Nto do without a sakabatou?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Himura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Step into it quicker.\NDon't rely upon your arm strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't finish before lunch at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, why must we do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time for this crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That man...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to hurry and find Kenshin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you learning the sword\Nfrom Kenshin Himura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't be stupid! My sword is\Nthat of Kamiya Kasshin-ryuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,lts sword is meant to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lump it together with battou-jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you chasing after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave that goofball to his own devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenshin... Do you know Kenshin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! How do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.47,0:21:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, we party!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But weren't you just drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,While away from his master,\Nmy pupil has been growing and maturing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a rather pleasing thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He has finally obtained what he\Nonce lacked with the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:22:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up! You can't fight\Nwithout a sword, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Seiku lives in an age of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not my right to destroy that peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.87,0:22:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A-are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.55,0:22:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Io... Iori was taken from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.72,0:22:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why would someone do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The man said he wanted your father's\Nlast sword... And then he!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.06,0:22:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This happened... because I wanted a sakabatou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This and that are two different-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.84,0:22:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.65,0:23:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The poor thing! To think they dumped\NShakku's last work out in these boonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it! Don't pull my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.49,0:23:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang, I don't much care for babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep hurtin' me,\NI'll cut you down in one fell swoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.50,0:23:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Broom! Broom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.43,0:23:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I seriously don't like ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Iori!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.73,0:23:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Iori!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let that babe go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.87,0:23:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So I take it yer the\Ninfamous Hitokiri Battousai?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You want Shakku's last piece, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.35,0:23:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary! Yer scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill ya right quick and then test\NShakku's famous blade on that baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura, you don't have a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's using his sheath against\Nsomeone with a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I must never offer the sword to that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:24:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The light shining forth from Himura's eyes...\Nhas vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.61,0:24:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura's eyes had seemed so gentle,\Nyet battle has turned him into a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.16,0:24:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitokiri Battousai...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.16,0:24:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, weren't ya against killin' people?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.46,0:24:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.23,0:24:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So ya can do anything ya want so long\Nas it don't kill me? Ain't you nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.24,0:24:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my job to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.44,0:24:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but somewhere along the line, I forced\Nthe tainted name "Hitokiri" on Shishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.94,0:24:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.61,0:24:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But now... I shall accept the taint unto myself;
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.42,0:24:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the taint needed to protect a world of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.49,0:24:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no! That is just-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.26,0:24:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A contradiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.00,0:24:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Iori!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.70,0:24:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank the Heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.80,0:24:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Iori...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.00,0:25:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That was really awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.04,0:25:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If yer totally empty-handed,\NI actually stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.32,0:25:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The taint... needed to defend the{\i}\N{\i1}peace and protect our loved ones...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.23,0:25:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father, I... I want to defend our peace!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.47,0:25:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... But...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.08,0:25:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now ya can't run around and\Ndodge my blows, can ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.08,0:25:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.82,0:25:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,For you! This blade was meant for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.59,0:25:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That is Shakku's final masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.73,0:26:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.70,0:26:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.60,0:26:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...a sakabatou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.04,0:26:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shakabato!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.57,0:26:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Shakku, I shall live by your ideals!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.11,0:26:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.39,0:26:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura, you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.72,0:26:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's okay. Broom Head didn't drop dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.43,0:26:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Broom! Broom!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.30,0:26:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make sure that you\Nget turned over to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.10,0:26:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.27,0:26:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The unvarnished wood simply couldn't\Nwithstand the power of your attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.81,0:26:55.34,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(432,396)}KEISHIN.\NSLAYING MYSELF,\NMY FORGED BLADES AMASS.\NHATED BY MY CHILD,\NI DO THIS FOR MY\NGRANDCHILD'S FUTURE.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.81,0:26:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Slaying myself, my forged blades amass..."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.99,0:26:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hated by my child,\NI do this for my grandchild's future."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.42,0:27:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura, after seeing you in battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.73,0:27:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe I understand my father a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.63,0:27:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This sakabatou is the embodiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.60,0:27:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the way you, Himura, and my father lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.08,0:27:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura, my father longed for the coming of\Na peaceful world more than anyone, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.52,0:27:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet even so, he lived amidst the turmoil\Nduring the end of the Shogunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.35,0:27:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He could neither pull back nor\Nstop to consider his actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.69,0:27:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He had no choice but to\Ncontinue making swords to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.66,0:27:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He had no choice but to go directly against\Nhis wishes... to live a contradicting life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.10,0:27:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet even so, he accepted that contradicting\Nlifestyle because he wished to protect someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.71,0:27:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Himura?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.71,0:27:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Seiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.35,0:27:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The sakabatou, Keishin. Please take it with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.12,0:28:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that is what my\Nfather would have wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.46,0:28:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, it is what I need most of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.63,0:28:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall humbly accept your kind offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.56,0:28:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.06,0:28:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Humbwee! Humbwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.23,0:28:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura ish humbwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.14,0:28:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's saying, "humbly"!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.51,0:28:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, let's go to Aoi-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.21,0:28:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you to Gramps and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.85,0:28:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I am confident they will help...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.48,0:28:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.59,0:28:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It is time we parted ways, Miss Misao.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.52,0:28:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,From this point on,\NI must fight this battle on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.93,0:28:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misao, I must not...\Ndraw you further into my affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.90,0:28:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? This is nothing!\NI don't care if I get caught up in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.74,0:29:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-that's right! You still haven't told\Nme anything about Master Aoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.38,0:29:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Han'nya...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.55,0:29:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikijo, Beshimi and Hyottoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.75,0:29:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the guys from the Oniwaban!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.36,0:29:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them... have passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.56,0:29:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.70,0:29:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them? Because they\Ngot tangled up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.97,0:29:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't kill people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.47,0:29:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not directly bring an end their lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.47,0:29:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, if they had not chosen to fight me,\Ntheir lives would not have been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.82,0:29:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura Battousai!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.27,0:30:31.50,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(732,450)}RESTAURANT AND INN\NAOI-YA{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.14,0:30:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.85,0:30:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Misao!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.29,0:30:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.52,0:30:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, uh, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.06,0:30:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.29,0:30:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If-if you mean Okina...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.07,0:31:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Misao...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.87,0:31:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me. Come on, Omasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.41,0:31:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Gramps go?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.64,0:31:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If Gramps pulled out his old\Nshinobi uniform and weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.75,0:31:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,then this has to be something serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.85,0:31:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The preparations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.32,0:31:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've burdened you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.09,0:31:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is within the capacity of a woman\Nsuch as I, who cannot fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.53,0:31:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.56,0:31:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have faith in my subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.76,0:31:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I could not entrust this to anyone but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.87,0:31:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can leave everything in your able hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.40,0:31:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You chose me not for my appearance,\Nbut for who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.37,0:31:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Shishio...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.78,0:31:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That certainly took you a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.91,0:31:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Slaying 50 men took some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.85,0:31:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely said to keep an eye on Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.92,0:32:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not on a child's errand.\NI merely did this on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.93,0:32:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifty men. As you can imagine,\NI am still throbbing with excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.56,0:32:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,May I request a reward for\Ncompleting my errand?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.20,0:32:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.64,0:32:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no interest in taking this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.41,0:32:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is to take your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.91,0:32:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Usui!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.74,0:32:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.24,0:32:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a man's privilege to take that\Nwhich he desires with his own might.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.62,0:32:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall face you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.28,0:32:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I just so happened to be\Nitching for a fight myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.15,0:32:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us fight until we are fully satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.29,0:32:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Shishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.27,0:32:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you faring, Himura?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.50,0:32:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajime Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.51,0:32:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumor has it that your\Nsakabatou has been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.98,0:32:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in Kyoto, do you keep your oath not to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.78,0:33:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,True, I have kept my oath. But that is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.35,0:33:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could have the honor of seeing the\NHitokiri Battousai here in Kyoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.02,0:33:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it would make for a most pleasant sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.13,0:33:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, the fifty police officers I enlisted\Nin the fight to subdue Shishio were murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.87,0:33:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened shortly after I issued their orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.54,0:33:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone must have been watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.37,0:33:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I have some information from Chou,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.54,0:33:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the member of Shishio's faction that\Nyou captured this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.05,0:33:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Please deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.35,0:33:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Goro Fujita, the one placed\Nin charge of torturing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.02,0:33:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer Hajime Saito! Didn't ya used\Nto serve in the Shinsengumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.53,0:33:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And speakin' of Shinsengumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.33,0:33:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,y'all are famous for putting poor old\NFurutaka under cruel torture
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.63,0:33:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to make him fess up before\Nthe lkeda-ya Incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.84,0:33:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You ain't the guy who did the dirty deed, are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.08,0:34:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You are lucky. That was absolutely correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.68,0:34:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too much! I ain't the type to tough it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.92,0:34:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I snitch, Master Shishio'll kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.72,0:34:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So if yer willin' to protect me,\NI'll tell ya anything ya wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.89,0:34:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, I will guarantee your safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.89,0:34:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt anything could best the\Npower of the state. Talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.03,0:34:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep me safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.17,0:34:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Shishio's plan is\Nbased upon the scenario
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.57,0:34:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,written by the radical loyalists\Nfrom the lkeda-ya Incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.01,0:34:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He intends to set Kyoto afire,\Nassassinate the leaders of the Shogunate,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.41,0:34:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and take the emperor to Choshu.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.18,0:34:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a massive plan to set the\Nthousand-year capital on fire
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.92,0:34:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,since they didn't pull it off last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.92,0:34:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got 500 subordinates who will\Nspread fires all across Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.09,0:34:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,During the confusion of the fire, they will\Nassassinate all of the civil servants in Kyoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.86,0:34:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He has taken measures for the\Nloyalists that burned him
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.23,0:34:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to get a taste of the major offense they had\Nattempted during the end of the Shogunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.60,0:35:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha think? Whether you\Nbelieve me or not is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.74,0:35:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was all bullshit, yer welcome to\Ndo whatever ya like with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.88,0:35:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't like I can run away or hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.95,0:35:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.05,0:35:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have information that verifies your statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.82,0:35:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What you said can be trusted,\Nbut I doubt that is the whole of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.46,0:35:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to avoid a repeat of\Nwhat happened in lkeda-ya at all costs,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.93,0:35:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,assuming Shishio is not a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.43,0:35:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It is only natural that you don't know more.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.10,0:35:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A careless slip of the tongue,\Nand the plan would fall to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.14,0:35:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were in Shishio's shoes, I would\NNEVER disclose important information
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.64,0:35:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that could affect the success of the operation\Nwith an untrustworthy subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.28,0:35:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Shishio ain't like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.68,0:35:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I woulda followed him\Nif he was such a narrow-minded prick!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.62,0:35:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so do you know what is\Ngoing on behind the scenes?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.66,0:35:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet! Everyone's in on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.16,0:35:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if ya tortured me, I ain't talkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.29,0:36:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be the same as betrayin' Master Shishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.97,0:36:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone can gloss over the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.54,0:36:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot deny the possibility\Nthat you were fed false information.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.87,0:36:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That ain't true! I saw it with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.98,0:36:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right in the Port of Osaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.55,0:36:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all I needed to know. You saved me\Nthe trouble of having to torture you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.22,0:36:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.32,0:36:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Kyoto Fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.23,0:36:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He will topple the people's trust\Nin the government
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.13,0:36:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,by burning what has been ingrained in the hearts\Nof the Japanese as the symbol of our capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.64,0:36:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Shishio's declaration of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.37,0:36:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the other scheme that he kept secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.34,0:36:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I will stop him.\NI take it you have no objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.58,0:36:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Himura Battousai?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.19,0:37:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your desire for information on Himura\Nhas led you to attack your old hideout, Aoi-ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.16,0:37:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You have grown twisted!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.43,0:37:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It is too late to hammer out your distortions!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.50,0:37:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I must crush you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.44,0:37:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy. They are fighting for keeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.01,0:37:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.72,0:37:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Shishio intends to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.05,0:37:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And here Usui could prove\Nto be a powerful asset.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.59,0:37:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It is fine, Sou.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.62,0:37:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is his form... of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.26,0:37:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To stop the Great Kyoto Fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.20,0:37:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we will need the assistance\Nof a group that knows Kyoto well.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.14,0:37:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.60,0:37:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fight a group with a group," is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.54,0:37:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,lt'd be great if you could find\Nreplacements for the fifty men I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.62,0:38:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the outcome will prove promising
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.58,0:38:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,if I further confuse a heart already in turmoil\Nas you resist returning to your Hitokiri ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.46,0:38:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Two people have followed you here from Tokyo.\NThey have already arrived in Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.42,0:38:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it in...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.46,0:38:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.50,0:38:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Never appear before me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.38,0:39:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it, Usui? Were you boiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.52,0:39:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.52,0:39:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not done yet.\NSee how I burn before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.72,0:39:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I will show you directly through those\Nfestering eyes, not through your Mind's Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.19,0:39:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.66,0:39:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.16,0:39:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your... body... as it burns in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.20,0:39:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That is exactly what I desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.84,0:39:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahiko! Yahiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.38,0:39:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! Where could he have gone? He ran off...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.41,0:40:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Officer Fujita! What impeccable timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.42,0:40:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a man in custody\Nwho picked a massive fight in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.02,0:40:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's terribly insistent that I let him see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.92,0:40:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he said you know each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.20,0:40:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.80,0:40:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of blindly searching around,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.03,0:40:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I just needed to get in trouble\Nwith the cops to catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.47,0:40:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Meeting up that way is a whole lot faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.81,0:40:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was you after all, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.98,0:40:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pfft, course it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.91,0:40:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Sanosuke Sagara's\Ngrand arrival in Kyoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.82,0:40:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenshin...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.89,0:40:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ummm, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.12,0:40:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.06,0:40:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.99,0:41:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.83,0:41:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Partly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.06,0:41:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.83,0:41:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My other half says,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.64,0:41:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.95,0:41:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys! Why are you enjoying some\Nemotional reunion without me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.92,0:41:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you just had to wander off somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.69,0:41:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nature called! Figure that out\Nfor yourself, Ms. Dense!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.66,0:41:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to pee isn't all that\Nembarrassing for a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.20,0:41:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be straightforward about it, Yahiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.20,0:41:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still going through puberty!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.03,0:41:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Or so you'd like to think! You're still a little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.97,0:41:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You suffer embarrassment as you mature!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.32,0:41:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just... don't know anymore!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.69,0:42:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is no stopping now!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.69,0:42:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Neither for you, nor me...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.00,0:42:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you can stop me, I dare you to try!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.34,0:42:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can no longer turn back.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.48,0:42:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until I defeat him,{\i}\N{\i1}my battle will not come to an end.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.69,0:42:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... will never leave your side again.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.51,0:42:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cannot see what lays ahead,{\i}\N{\i1}I will keep walking...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.88,0:42:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...with this sword.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.71,0:43:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Kaze nara yurusou\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}If it were the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.78,0:43:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Nani mo kamo\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}All would be forgiven
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.63,0:43:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Sayakeshi nijizora\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}The vibrant rainbow in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.77,0:43:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Tokete yuku\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Begins to dissipate
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.98,0:44:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Ishidatami ni wa\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}On the stone pavement
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.99,0:44:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Okizari no hana\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}There is a deserted flower
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.96,0:44:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Semete daite yaritakute\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}At the very least, I want to embrace it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.97,0:44:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Ato sukoshi utsukushikereba\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}If it were a little more beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.98,0:44:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Orarezu ni ikita darou ka\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Could it have lived without getting plucked?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.99,0:44:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Itazura ni yume no inochi wo\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Who is the one that mischievously
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.97,0:45:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Kimeru no wa dare darou\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Determined its life's dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.71,0:45:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Katamuku hoshi-tachi\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Sinking stars
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.72,0:45:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Soba ni ite\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Stay by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.69,0:45:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Yoake wa nana iro\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}The dawn has seven colors
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.77,0:45:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Dare no tame\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}But who are they for?
